- Stan code for fitting the two cluster model

Functions.R
- Functions for the real-time update of patient status and trajectories

plot_table_preparation.R
- Prepare the parameter posterior draws, called in plot_beta_summaries.R, plot_groupmeantraj_Figure2.R, plot_real time update_2 cluster model shared Beta funtional Theta 230124_scl70.R, plot_sankey.R, and Tables 2 and 3_plot_table_beta_summaries_sharedbeta_scl70.R

plot_beta_summaries.R
- Create Nightingale plot for biomarker-specific fixed effects coefficients

plot_groupmeantraj_Figure2.R
- Create cluster-specific mean biomarker trajectories plot

plot_ns_splines.R
- Visualize the natural splines, included in the supplementary material

plot_real time update_2 cluster model shared Beta funtional Theta 230124_scl70.R
- Create demonstration plot for person-specific real-time update of biomarker trajectories

plot_sankey.R
- Create the Sankey plot in the manuscript

Table1.R
- Table 1 in the manuscript, description of SSc cohort

table_clustersummary.R
- Table 1 in the manuscript, cluster-specific summaries

Tables 2 and 3_plot_table_beta_summaries_sharedbeta_scl70.R
- Nightingale plots (and corresponding tables) of fix effects coefficients by cluster and outcome
